<HEADLINE>
<P>
SCHABARUM WON'T RUN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I have known Sarah Flores for the last 10 years and have been quite impressed 
with the devotion and loyalty she had for Schabarum. 
</P>
<P>
It is quite all right for Schabarum to endorse whomever he wants to succeed 
him. But it was so sickening of him to be so unkind to Flores who has been such 
a loyal and trusted secretary and deputy for 18 years ("Schabarum Snubs Aide 
and Backs Judge as His Successor," Part B, March 16). 
</P>
<P>
It will be interesting to note how Schabarum could attract loyal friends and 
associates in his future endeavors in Southern California. 
</P>
<P>
VICTOR S. SY 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
