by Sen. Gary K. Hart (D-Santa Barbara) to ban cigarette vending machines except 
in locations not accessible to minors. Violations would have called for $1,000 
merchant fines. A 2-5 vote was cast on the bill. Six yes votes were required 
for approval. 
</P>
<P>
Bill Introductions: 
</P>
<P>
