<P>
ROAD PROJECT CLOSES LANES AT INTERSECTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The city has temporarily closed left turn lanes on eastbound Yorba Linda 
Boulevard at Imperial Highway to complete a $1.1-million street improvement 
project. 
</P>
<P>
The Yorba Linda Boulevard Beautification Project includes widening the streets, 
constructing median islands and installing decorative crosswalks at the 
intersection. The construction began this week and is scheduled to continue 
through mid-May. 
</P>
