ORANGE COUNTY -- AGRICULTURE; PESTICIDES; INSECTS; DEUKMEJIAN, GEORGE; PUBLIC 
HEALTH; PUBLIC SAFETY; MALATHION; PEST CONTROL; HEALTH HAZARDS; ORANGE COUNTY 
BOARD OF SUPERVISORS 
</P>
